data.description: ***SHORT SALE***  Welcome Home!!  4 Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath home located in Central York School District is waiting for you!! This lovely home features a beautiful custom front door and a charming wrap-around porch. The large remodeled kitchen has a double wall oven, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and recessed lighting. The large family room features hardwood floors, a cathedral ceiling with beautiful skylights. The living room is spacious with spectacular views from the large windows. The formal dining room features chair rails, Crown molding & Built-ins. The upstairs has a primary Bedroom and full primary bathroom and plenty of closet space. There are 3 additional Bedrooms and another full bath to complete the upper level. The backyard is perfect for entertaining family and friends all year around! Lastly, this home has an attached 2-car garage and enough space to park four additional small to mid-size vehicles in the driveway! Do not miss your opportunity to call this home!! The home does need a little TLC/Cosmetics. This is an awesome opportunity to be able to call this place home!! Schedule your appointment today!
